卡拉‧巴蒂優‧科羅納多（Carla Badillo
Coronado）在她的部落格[「女人大陸」](http://mujerentierrafirme.blogspot.com/2010/08/la-
negritud-luminosa-del-valle-del.html
"http://mujerentierrafirme.blogspot.com/2010/08/la-negritud-luminosa-del-
valle-del.html")以[綢塔山谷](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Valle_del_Chota
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Valle_del_Chota")的[非裔厄瓜多人](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afro-
Ecuadorian_people "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afro-
Ecuadorian_people")為題，發表了一系列照片。

